Dialogue: 0,1:50:01.81,1:50:08.91,ED-chs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\blur5}满溢的光辉
Dialogue: 0,1:50:09.33,1:50:12.70,ED-chs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\blur5}洒在银河里
Dialogue: 0,1:50:13.04,1:50:20.77,ED-chs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\blur5}多么的美丽
Dialogue: 0,1:50:44.14,1:50:52.64,ED-chs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\blur5}满怀着爱意  开始迈步
Dialogue: 0,1:50:52.98,1:50:58.96,ED-chs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\blur5}就像奏起歌谣
Dialogue: 0,1:50:59.06,1:51:09.86,ED-chs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\blur5}我相信  哪怕斗转星移
Dialogue: 0,1:51:09.97,1:51:21.11,ED-chs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\blur5}太阳一定会升起  一定
Dialogue: 0,1:51:34.83,1:51:41.27,ED-chs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\blur5}面朝着星星
