Dialogue: 0,1:51:49.36,1:51:56.51,ED-chs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\blur5}我又看到那
Dialogue: 0,1:51:56.83,1:52:00.08,ED-chs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\blur5}满溢的温柔
Dialogue: 0,1:52:00.61,1:52:09.33,ED-chs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\blur5}脸庞的微笑
Dialogue: 0,1:52:42.63,1:52:58.33,ED-chs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\blur5}有什么藏在  你的胸口？
Dialogue: 0,1:53:01.54,1:53:10.04,ED-chs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\blur5}请化作爱意  继续向前
