Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.20,0:01:26.81,旁白/独白 - chs,旁白/独白,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}百年不易  究其一生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.13,0:01:43.93,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玛琪娅！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.64,0:01:49.47,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.14,0:01:52.59,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在干什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.10,0:01:54.83,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再这么玩下去  工作就做不完了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.17,0:01:59.13,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}呐  玛琪娅也来嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.31,0:02:00.52,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快飞过来！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.35,0:02:04.66,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我…  我做不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.55,0:02:08.44,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}胆小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.66,0:02:12.40,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玛琪娅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.84,0:02:14.80,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不用理那个野姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.17,0:02:15.76,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}克里姆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.76,0:02:19.78,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅她  真的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.37,0:02:35.44,旁白/独白 - chs,旁白/独白,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}远离人世  以织布为生的她们  世人称之为
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.18,0:02:39.65,旁白/独白 - chs,旁白/独白,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}「离别一族」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.80,0:02:47.36,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么了  拉希璐长老
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.93,0:02:50.59,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.85,0:02:54.71,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玛琪娅  下次一定要飞哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.08,0:03:00.04,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.75,0:03:02.29,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你回来啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.32,0:03:06.65,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不能那样把布随便乱扔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.60,0:03:08.83,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对不起啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.52,0:03:10.77,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瞧你都湿透了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.24,0:03:13.04,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}爸爸  采到好花了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.23,0:03:15.54,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯  应该能调出鲜明的颜色来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.15,0:03:20.17,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玛琪娅  再见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.72,0:03:21.77,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.63,0:03:28.68,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再见…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.97,0:03:36.93,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}纱竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.22,0:03:52.77,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么在哭啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.82,0:03:56.39,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为我总是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.01,0:03:59.60,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一个人？  我不是在这吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.60,0:04:02.16,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}长老大人  不是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.77,0:04:06.13,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你真的是个爱哭鬼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.52,0:04:11.66,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}知道我们为什么被叫做离别一族吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.49,0:04:18.26,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}容颜不改  长生于世的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.89,0:04:20.85,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对于其他人来说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.96,0:04:22.86,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就好像传说中的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.37,0:04:26.58,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过数百年前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.17,0:04:29.39,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样的存在还遍布世间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.24,0:04:32.69,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}形似飞鸟的翼人一族
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.53,0:04:35.50,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拂晓时分歌唱的花儿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.39,0:04:39.82,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}巨大的鱼儿负着行李破浪前行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.18,0:04:41.85,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.85,0:04:46.94,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们都已经  告别了这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.26,0:04:51.33,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.82,0:04:54.55,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们才与机枢为邻  织下「昔日织」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.97,0:04:58.37,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要生活在这里  你就不会孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.38,0:05:00.88,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}漫长的年岁里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.19,0:05:03.40,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那些不觉中随风而去的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.82,0:05:05.64,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「昔日织」会帮你铭记
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.01,0:05:10.01,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那些不得不与之别过的人儿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.08,0:05:14.37,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「昔日织」会伴你饮泣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.18,0:05:17.60,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}伴我…  饮泣？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.14,0:05:20.23,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然而  如果
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.74,0:05:22.94,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有朝一日你离开了伊尔夫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.53,0:05:28.40,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在外面的世界与人相遇相识
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.70,0:05:31.24,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}绝对不能爱上别人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.39,0:05:35.46,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这份爱  真的会让你孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.46,0:05:41.04,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和人相识了  也会孤身一人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.65,0:05:43.16,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这就是我们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.70,0:05:47.51,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}离别一族  无可抉择的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.01,0:05:52.22,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.62,0:05:54.27,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}晚安  玛琪娅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.26,0:05:58.40,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要忘记  织下今天的「昔日织」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.70,0:05:59.43,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.72,0:07:28.69,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}花开了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.42,0:07:45.23,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玛琪娅？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.99,0:07:56.71,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雷纳托！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.02,0:08:00.27,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那  梅萨特要…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.74,0:08:01.39,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玛琪娅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.86,0:08:03.22,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快去向长老大人报告！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.56,0:08:09.64,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}长老！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.41,0:08:26.53,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}长老！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.48,0:08:31.45,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}长老…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.38,0:08:34.70,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}长老！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.70,0:08:35.91,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雷纳托是全副武装的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.11,0:08:37.45,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}保护好昔日织！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.47,0:09:17.89,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还真如传闻所说  完全就是些小鬼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.13,0:09:21.67,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂  你这家伙不就好这口吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.82,0:09:22.60,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都退下！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.67,0:09:24.65,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}伊萨尔师团长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.03,0:09:41.37,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们的村长呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.49,0:09:47.40,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.59,0:09:49.99,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.84,0:09:52.20,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}虽然貌似少女
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.54,0:09:56.96,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我听说  您其实是活了400多岁的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.16,0:10:01.59,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我等以机枢为邻  继日梭织
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.97,0:10:03.75,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只是如此的循环往复
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.58,0:10:06.52,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}又如何能与尔等交集…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.52,0:10:08.56,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这不是你能决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.26,0:10:11.67,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是王的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.10,0:10:15.44,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还请各位  随我们前往梅萨特的王宫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.10,0:10:17.81,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不许接近拉希璐长老！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.24,0:10:21.97,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要女的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.38,0:10:23.36,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把女的都抓起来！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.32,0:10:27.17,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}胆敢反抗者  无须犹疑一概格杀！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.62,0:10:38.08,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这家伙也得赤眼病了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.76,0:10:44.62,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不用理会！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.07,0:10:46.55,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}先去抓伊尔夫的女人！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.61,0:10:58.26,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}放我出去！ 放我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.53,0:11:30.18,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玛琪娅！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.19,0:12:49.99,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.42,0:12:55.92,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.84,0:13:23.98,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}呐  玛琪娅也来嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.43,0:13:25.70,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快飞过来！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.58,0:14:09.20,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小…  小宝宝？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.34,0:14:10.82,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以泪作酒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.06,0:14:16.18,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}口中微咸风味别致呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.60,0:14:21.12,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是长老身边的玛琪娅吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.58,0:14:25.97,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}本来还想收购一些昔日织  看来得就此止步了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.16,0:14:30.56,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这个流浪者的村落  似乎被盗贼给袭击了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.33,0:14:33.62,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你看  小家伙才呱呱坠地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.09,0:14:42.18,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是伟大啊  老妈这一类人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.46,0:14:45.02,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}死了都还保护着小家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.37,0:14:49.24,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嘛  如此过不了多久  两人就能在天堂再会了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.68,0:14:51.78,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小家伙的昔日织  也就到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.94,0:14:56.08,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过是一点儿  连布都算不上的残片罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.94,0:14:59.62,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嘛  总比孤身一人好得多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.24,0:15:04.10,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他真的是孤身一人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.53,0:15:38.83,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好大的…  力气…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.85,0:15:41.73,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好大…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.55,0:15:44.41,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}算了吧  算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.75,0:15:54.61,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你还打算带他走吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.85,0:15:57.84,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这可不是玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.84,0:15:58.93,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他不是玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.64,0:16:01.35,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.77,0:16:05.02,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}昔日织啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.51,0:16:08.80,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这下可好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.04,0:16:12.11,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}孤身一人的她遇到了孤苦无靠的他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.17,0:16:19.00,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}冷吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.89,0:16:32.04,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}奇怪的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.01,0:16:35.43,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太阳公公的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.91,0:16:46.33,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.67,0:16:48.08,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我在这儿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.60,0:16:48.58,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\an3\blur3}站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.98,0:16:52.49,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}朗格！戴奥尔！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.65,0:16:54.07,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们还敢偷懒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.58,0:16:56.57,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}来追我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.06,0:16:57.06,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\an3\blur3}站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.17,0:16:58.30,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我才不呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.37,0:17:00.28,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是的  这两个淘气鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.42,0:17:03.54,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么了  奥诺拉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.77,0:17:20.78,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}奶子…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.30,0:17:23.32,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}奶子…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.10,0:17:25.44,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}奶子要怎么…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.24,0:17:28.39,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.22,0:17:34.49,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.20,0:17:38.79,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小孩子要养育小婴儿  这怎么可能呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.93,0:17:44.70,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是  你的孩子吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.90,0:17:52.69,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}伊尔夫  不是看不出年龄的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.19,0:17:53.90,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是你的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.45,0:17:57.89,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}朗格  戴奥尔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.61,0:18:01.33,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我…  我才15岁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.89,0:18:03.53,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这孩子…  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.22,0:18:05.13,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.32,0:18:16.59,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这孩子叫什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.00,0:18:19.11,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.10,0:18:21.19,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.59,0:18:22.75,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怪女人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.05,0:18:24.47,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怪宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.52,0:18:25.47,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.70,0:18:28.58,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.52,0:18:30.77,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是女孩的名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.26,0:18:32.26,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他不是男孩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.51,0:18:33.86,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那…  那就
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.13,0:18:34.88,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.00,0:18:36.60,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾利…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.76,0:18:37.66,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾利尔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.00,0:18:39.98,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾利尔！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.15,0:18:40.88,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.38,0:18:41.83,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.83,0:18:42.48,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哈哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.62,0:18:44.43,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是的  行了行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.99,0:18:53.33,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她是我亲戚的孩子  会织布
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.43,0:19:05.38,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}店里有个没人用的织布机
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.78,0:19:07.23,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}用它就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.92,0:19:13.70,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}去外边等我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.23,0:19:18.79,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是伊尔夫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.64,0:19:21.48,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}达雷尔  真是瞒不过你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.70,0:19:22.48,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还请…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.15,0:19:28.46,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}伊尔夫的布能卖个好价钱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.51,0:19:31.84,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这可是难得的摇钱树
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.09,0:19:33.88,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算别人求我  也不会跟他说的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.04,0:19:36.18,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.50,0:19:39.37,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过  你本来就过得很困难了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.97,0:19:42.20,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还要多一个伊尔夫的小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.77,0:19:43.56,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.17,0:19:46.60,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也不知道今后还会发生什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.38,0:19:49.83,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不论有她  还是没她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.02,0:19:58.00,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}给您  这周的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.06,0:20:00.13,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一直以来谢谢你喽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.24,0:20:06.06,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你家的奶酪可是别有一番风味呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.06,0:20:08.80,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哪里哪里  下周也请您多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.02,0:20:11.62,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看来  有两番风味呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.62,0:20:13.06,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那下下周还请您关照
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.13,0:20:16.63,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}像我这样的大妈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.77,0:20:19.47,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一个人带孩子也是手忙脚乱的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.37,0:20:21.44,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你知道吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.79,0:20:25.01,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我丈夫他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.10,0:20:28.68,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}被得了赤眼病的雷纳托给杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.67,0:20:34.01,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.84,0:20:36.42,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}又是「我不知道」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.40,0:20:39.51,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所谓的妈妈到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.05,0:20:41.52,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为我  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.74,0:20:43.71,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.79,0:20:46.10,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是我这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.46,0:22:02.26,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能走了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.31,0:22:03.79,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好棒啊  艾利尔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.91,0:22:05.81,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾利尔！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.52,0:22:10.54,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好棒啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.77,0:22:12.32,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾利尔好棒啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.50,0:22:21.16,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你啊  完全就是个妈妈了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.56,0:22:25.59,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是…  妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.49,0:22:29.77,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哪有这样不靠谱的妈妈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.70,0:22:33.59,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们两个  羊圈打扫完了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.81,0:22:34.96,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}糟了  是妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.07,0:22:36.02,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快走吧  戴奥尔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.84,0:22:40.05,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.18,0:22:41.33,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.78,0:22:43.26,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}过来  屁股撅起来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.23,0:22:44.90,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.20,0:22:46.23,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.46,0:22:53.22,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}叫一声…  妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.30,0:22:57.97,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不算  刚才的不算！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.84,0:22:59.68,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈 妈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.19,0:23:03.37,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾利尔  你刚才说了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.69,0:23:07.64,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再叫一声
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.88,0:23:10.68,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再叫一声  好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.26,0:23:21.75,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}又一头雷纳托赤眼病发作了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.20,0:23:24.48,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}已经即时处分
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.69,0:23:26.95,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}并隔离焚化了尸体
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.19,0:23:28.90,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}之后埋于地下深处
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.31,0:23:31.48,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}目前存活的还有5头
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.75,0:23:34.04,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊  这该如何是好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.42,0:23:38.11,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}多年以来  我梅萨特之所以能鼎镇诸国
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.33,0:23:41.39,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}正是缘于上古的神兽  翔空的雷纳特
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.96,0:23:45.18,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果雷纳特就此灭绝  这份平衡恐怕会难以维系
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.55,0:23:49.03,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为维护我梅萨特的权威
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.03,0:23:53.28,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}必须找到能够代替雷纳特的  超越人智的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.43,0:23:54.85,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是  是了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.20,0:23:56.96,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们不是已经得到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.13,0:23:58.64,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}天命之血！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.13,0:24:01.92,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}伊萨尔  那个小姑娘怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.29,0:24:05.71,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要成为海赛尔王妃的那个伊尔夫的小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.75,0:24:10.00,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}呐  为什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.20,0:24:13.42,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们明明拥有翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.37,0:24:16.41,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么不从这里飞走呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.45,0:24:23.37,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}胆小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.92,0:24:26.95,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为自己终究会死
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.86,0:24:32.16,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就任凭心底那往日之思灼烧胸口  焚化身躯
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.58,0:24:34.05,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只是因为自己终究会死…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.27,0:24:38.13,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅大人  王要召见你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.70,0:24:40.67,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.57,0:24:45.32,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅大人  为何您一直在此？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.14,0:24:49.05,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为这里像昔日织之塔
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.80,0:24:51.77,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.34,0:25:09.12,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}完成了！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.38,0:25:10.57,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}织上话语了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.67,0:25:13.27,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯  「奥诺拉  好起来」
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.79,0:25:17.75,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在我出生的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.30,0:25:21.36,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是用文字  而是靠织布来传递心意的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.91,0:25:23.57,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈出生的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.99,0:25:25.78,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我出生的地方呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.84,0:25:28.68,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蒂塔的妈妈说了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.79,0:25:31.00,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈和大家不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.14,0:25:35.15,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾利尔出生的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.74,0:25:37.79,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是用肚皮说话的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.14,0:25:39.59,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}毛毛虫啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.80,0:25:40.80,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}过来啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.80,0:25:41.51,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}爬来爬去  爬来爬去
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.51,0:25:43.89,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}肚皮说的话不就是放屁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.17,0:25:48.44,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}奥诺拉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.18,0:25:50.72,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}轻轻给它盖上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.64,0:25:57.08,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还不错吧  奥诺拉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.34,0:26:01.64,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}爸爸妈妈结婚的时候奥诺拉就来我们家了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.50,0:26:05.62,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是算成人的年龄  差不多都要90岁了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.87,0:26:19.69,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾利尔的妈妈  可奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.80,0:26:21.98,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}总是偷偷摸摸的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.12,0:26:23.50,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}才不奇怪呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.73,0:26:24.42,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.16,0:26:26.20,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}母亲她…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.98,0:26:27.67,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人家…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.97,0:26:30.48,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还叫自己「人家」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.48,0:26:32.83,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就像小宝宝在撒娇
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.95,0:26:34.80,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾利尔才奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.46,0:26:38.21,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}男孩怎么会喜欢妈妈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.29,0:26:40.25,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}才不奇怪呢  人家…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.57,0:26:43.33,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我  最讨厌了！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.96,0:26:45.47,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我喜欢妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.59,0:26:46.74,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.81,0:26:48.84,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也最讨厌蒂塔了！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.69,0:26:57.56,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你没事吧  蒂塔
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.79,0:27:05.96,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}挺不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.41,0:27:10.96,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}来  这个月的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.34,0:27:12.62,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.04,0:27:15.76,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对了  你能看一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.36,0:27:18.80,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有个客人带了昔日织过来
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.97,0:27:31.70,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.73,0:27:34.06,Sayo Asa - chs,昔日织,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&H115E8B&}于梅萨特之王城
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.87,0:27:37.03,Sayo Asa - chs,昔日织,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&H115E8B&}与王子结为连理
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.86,0:27:38.88,Sayo Asa - chs,昔日织,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&H115E8B&}美丽的…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.50,0:27:41.82,Sayo Asa - chs,昔日织,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&H115E8B&}蕾…莉雅…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.17,0:27:44.40,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂  玛琪娅！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.74,0:27:51.13,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}达雷尔说帮你问问能不能搭上货船
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.07,0:27:53.01,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你看  就是那孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.23,0:27:56.22,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}各种意义上来说  也到时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.94,0:27:59.93,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只是  艾利尔要怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.92,0:28:05.89,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}带着孩子长途跋涉  比你想象的还要辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.75,0:28:09.48,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且  你这样的还会被人嫌弃
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.36,0:28:13.07,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾利尔就让我们来照顾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.81,0:28:15.16,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.22,0:28:16.54,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.54,0:28:17.33,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾利尔！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.83,0:28:33.28,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥  埋得太深的话
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.52,0:28:34.15,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.57,0:28:36.19,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果  奥诺拉活过来…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.19,0:28:36.64,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.79,0:28:39.90,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}埋得太浅会被野狗刨出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.94,0:28:41.45,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.83,0:28:57.78,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是埋上土  就见不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.16,0:29:00.35,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要到这儿来  什么时候都能见到的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.14,0:29:03.24,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是埋上土  就不能玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.81,0:29:05.30,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好好夸夸它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.83,0:29:08.55,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没有一点痛苦  安然的死去了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.41,0:29:12.60,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大家都会迎来这一天的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.44,0:29:17.89,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}奥诺拉只是天生注定  要比我们更早的迎来这一天
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.05,0:29:23.79,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玛琪娅
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.12,0:29:26.17,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.58,0:29:31.18,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}呐
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.37,0:29:33.84,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大家都会死掉吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.56,0:29:35.18,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.52,0:29:36.48,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈也会？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.70,0:29:38.18,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.26,0:29:44.06,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玛琪娅
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.45,0:29:45.20,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.38,0:29:46.32,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.50,0:29:53.49,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾利尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.86,0:29:55.77,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还有大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.02,0:29:58.02,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都会比我…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.98,0:29:59.82,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}更早的…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.71,0:30:01.78,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}更早更早的…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.33,0:30:03.73,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}迎来这一天
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.09,0:30:04.77,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玛琪娅
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.75,0:30:07.82,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不是不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.50,0:30:09.85,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}虽然我早就知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.62,0:30:11.48,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.58,0:30:14.89,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}顺序什么的  怎么样都无所谓吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.74,0:30:17.70,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别哭啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.47,0:30:20.86,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}兰格你也会…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.18,0:30:24.77,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你如今  不是艾利尔的妈妈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.37,0:30:28.66,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈  是不会哭的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.82,0:30:29.99,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我家的那个妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.80,0:30:34.26,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}叫妈妈的人  一定都不会哭的！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.15,0:30:40.01,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不哭
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.02,0:30:42.36,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯  别哭
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.09,0:30:46.18,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要哭
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.25,0:30:49.06,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯  我没哭
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.26,0:30:54.06,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.29,0:30:55.10,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.62,0:31:00.39,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾利尔
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.26,0:31:09.59,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在等我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.56,0:31:11.80,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}乖乖去床上睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.22,0:31:20.56,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}变重了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.20,0:31:21.85,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.30,0:31:26.13,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}果然还是太阳公公的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.09,0:31:28.88,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不会再哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.66,0:31:31.44,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为我是艾利尔的妈妈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.50,0:31:35.89,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们今后  要一直在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.06,0:31:39.47,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}之前的事  对不起了…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.54,0:31:40.84,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}之前的事  对不起了…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.02,0:31:42.16,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}之前的事  对不起了…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.48,0:31:43.60,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}之前的事  对不起了…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.06,0:31:45.28,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}之前的事  对不起了…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.22,0:31:48.27,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}之前的事  对不起了…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.48,0:31:49.65,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}之前的事  对不起了…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.36,0:31:52.93,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾利尔他们  已经不在这了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.30,0:32:04.89,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不去送送她们吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.93,0:32:24.17,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我要去外边！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.27,0:32:26.31,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂  都说了不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.40,0:32:27.43,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾利尔！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.02,0:32:30.29,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是的  我们不是约好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.39,0:32:31.88,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}做一个安静的乖孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.78,0:32:34.34,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对…  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.42,0:32:38.28,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玛琪娅？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.15,0:32:43.85,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你还活着啊  玛琪娅！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.46,0:32:47.04,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你还…活着啊…  克里姆
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.37,0:32:55.31,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}梅萨特
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.89,0:32:58.88,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}盯上了我们伊尔夫子民的长命之血
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.81,0:33:01.16,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为此村子被袭击了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.27,0:33:03.04,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅也被…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.17,0:33:06.83,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈  蕾莉雅是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.22,0:33:08.98,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你让他叫你妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.87,0:33:11.00,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊  不是
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.10,0:33:13.02,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也不是  让他这么叫
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.29,0:33:14.49,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊  我没有生气
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.16,0:33:16.12,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也不是责备你
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.22,0:33:19.89,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只是  长老大人不是经常说…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.13,0:33:24.26,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯  我没忘
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.61,0:33:26.72,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.16,0:34:02.01,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明天早上  会举行王子成婚的庆祝游行
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.13,0:34:05.29,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}从王宫出发的王子的队伍
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.69,0:34:09.73,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为了和从离宫出发的蕾莉雅的队伍会合  一定会过桥
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.32,0:34:12.93,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们就在这里  袭击王子搭乘的雷纳托
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.26,0:34:14.25,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}制造混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.66,0:34:17.09,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}趁着离宫那边警备薄弱
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.99,0:34:19.67,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把蕾莉雅夺回来
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.80,0:34:23.54,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}游行  人家也想看
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.85,0:34:26.88,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯…抱歉了  下次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.97,0:34:28.69,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人家…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.57,0:34:31.12,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想回去！
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.57,0:34:32.48,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾利尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.15,0:34:37.70,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈  在这里的话就不像妈妈了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.33,0:34:46.28,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾利尔
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.00,0:34:48.84,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}毛毛虫啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.84,0:34:50.18,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}过来喽！
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.18,0:34:53.88,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}爬来爬去  爬来爬去…
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.00,0:35:19.14,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天乃是良辰吉日  都是好东西哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.04,0:35:32.10,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}将伊尔夫的血脉纳入王室的时刻  终于到来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.79,0:35:34.32,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雷纳特和伊尔夫
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.14,0:35:37.79,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这两个犹存于世的古老传说
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.42,0:35:41.04,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我等都已掌握在手
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.84,0:35:46.85,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我等天命所归  已是无人能敌！
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.83,0:35:56.35,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}随着海赛尔王子和蕾莉雅公主的成婚
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.77,0:36:01.54,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}新的传说必如向阳花木  光耀我梅萨特！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.62,0:37:16.33,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.83,0:37:32.89,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}刺客吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.06,0:37:34.01,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么回事！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.07,0:37:43.90,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅  蕾莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.10,0:37:54.74,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哦呦  抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.59,0:38:03.51,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.43,0:38:07.24,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玛琪娅
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.21,0:38:09.46,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你怎么在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.26,0:38:11.70,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}克里姆也来了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.11,0:38:14.13,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}克里姆他？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.25,0:38:15.57,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯  我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.79,0:38:17.47,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大家都在等着蕾莉雅…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.26,0:38:18.99,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.47,0:38:22.46,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我已经  回不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.43,0:38:24.23,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.84,0:38:26.98,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为我逃不掉
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.95,0:38:28.97,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.22,0:38:30.81,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅是那么的身手敏捷
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.08,0:38:32.05,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.18,0:38:34.58,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过是城堡的高墙而已  飞过去就…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.49,0:38:46.74,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我已经  不能再见克里姆了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.13,0:38:50.12,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.82,0:38:51.70,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.70,0:38:52.87,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.91,0:38:56.16,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快走  玛琪娅
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.21,0:38:58.69,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是  蕾莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.49,0:39:00.20,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快走！
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.47,0:39:02.74,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没事的  我不是会飞吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.84,0:39:04.72,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别让她跑了！
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.57,0:39:17.40,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.02,0:39:19.44,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}给我追！
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.44,0:39:19.94,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}站住
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.69,0:39:22.24,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们要是敢向她出手
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.74,0:39:34.76,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.12,0:39:43.95,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.57,0:39:46.21,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是会飞的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.82,0:39:55.49,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小家伙长大了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.01,0:39:59.20,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是还活着应该有6岁了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.70,0:40:02.65,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么样  外面的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.66,0:40:06.74,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你也是  伊尔夫
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.15,0:40:08.52,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一半是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.38,0:40:10.21,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拉希璐…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.78,0:40:11.72,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}长老她
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.99,0:40:15.56,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}之所以会禁止伊尔夫的子民离开村子
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.96,0:40:21.10,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是因为她知道  来到人世的伊尔夫会迎来何等命运
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.35,0:40:23.86,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哪怕本人不愿
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.95,0:40:27.50,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}身为异族的我等  免不了被人窃视  被人利用
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.47,0:40:31.01,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最后被人嫌恶  被人驱逐
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.28,0:40:32.91,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没错
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.36,0:40:38.53,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}离别一族  注定要与别离相依相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.27,0:40:45.02,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}愿你过一段好一点的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.53,0:41:06.18,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}克里姆  你的伤…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.53,0:41:14.28,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还是脱掉上衣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.62,0:41:22.15,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小婴儿  是什么样的？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.88,0:41:26.09,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}做母亲  是什么样…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.74,0:41:31.79,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我  算是母亲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.16,0:41:35.40,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不懂的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.80,0:41:37.33,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}米朵会教给我
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.56,0:41:40.00,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}会帮助我
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.55,0:41:42.32,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感觉就像弟弟一样
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.44,0:41:45.84,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是  又有点不同
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.46,0:41:51.12,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾利尔笑的话  我就会很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.08,0:41:52.85,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.49,0:41:56.79,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我在这儿  就能让艾利尔笑的话
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.54,0:41:59.58,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就想  一直和他在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.58,0:42:00.70,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你说的可真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.15,0:42:06.17,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明明艾利尔会先死
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.37,0:42:09.07,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明明艾利尔
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.02,0:42:11.80,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}会让玛琪娅孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.50,0:42:18.56,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不许惹她哭！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.56,0:42:19.82,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是的  艾利尔
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.28,0:42:22.07,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\an3\blur3}不许你惹妈妈哭！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.07,0:42:23.89,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾利尔  快住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.67,0:42:25.57,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}保护得了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.57,0:42:30.56,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你  所珍爱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.95,0:42:55.33,Sayo Asa - chs,昔日织,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&H115E8B&}我们要留在梅萨特  救出蕾莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.49,0:42:58.65,Sayo Asa - chs,昔日织,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&H115E8B&}带着孩子的你只会碍手碍脚
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.18,0:43:02.09,Sayo Asa - chs,昔日织,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&H115E8B&}所以  玛琪娅
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.32,0:43:04.16,Sayo Asa - chs,昔日织,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&H115E8B&}再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.36,0:43:08.71,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要回家吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.75,0:43:11.68,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们不回家的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.46,0:43:13.39,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那大家呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.68,0:43:18.69,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就我们两人去新的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.54,0:43:20.77,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}新的地方是
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.12,0:43:23.93,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}米朵和朗格哥哥他们都不在的地方吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.89,0:43:26.81,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.21,0:43:29.57,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不得不  和大家说再见呢
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.70,0:43:32.89,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我呢  只要妈妈在就好
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.98,0:43:38.16,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯  妈妈也是  只要有艾利尔在就好
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.16,0:43:40.35,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.81,0:43:42.44,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你啊  是有缘由的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.72,0:43:46.35,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是惹出事情然后溜个没影  那我可受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.22,0:43:50.08,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾利尔！
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.02,0:43:52.85,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.46,0:43:55.21,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂  给我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.42,0:43:56.32,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}臭小鬼！
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.41,0:43:59.74,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈要再去找找
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.10,0:44:01.71,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在旅店的房间乖乖等我
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.25,0:44:03.84,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.26,0:44:05.95,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}乖乖等我  求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.87,0:44:13.32,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.77,0:44:16.23,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们这主要是陪酒
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.43,0:44:18.10,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以多在夜里工作
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.30,0:44:19.02,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.32,0:44:21.94,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要在…  夜里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.30,0:44:23.44,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有问题？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.03,0:44:26.67,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的孩子…  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.27,0:44:29.03,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他还…很小
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.98,0:44:33.50,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}之前辞掉的小姑娘也是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.96,0:44:36.38,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小小年纪就…  还真是无忧无虑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.81,0:44:37.63,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.46,0:44:40.22,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是吗？  那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.68,0:44:42.89,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你就没有一点作为母亲的自觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.11,0:44:44.96,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}实在抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.66,0:44:48.66,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这里没有工作会交给你这种人
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.30,0:45:05.55,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}欢迎回来！
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.52,0:45:08.36,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我回来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.28,0:45:12.85,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈  快看快看
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.97,0:45:14.46,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个啊  昔日织…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.45,0:45:22.16,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别给我添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.77,0:45:25.61,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么要擅自把它拿出来？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.57,0:45:30.36,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}呐  快看嘛  妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.36,0:45:32.44,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么你就是不听话呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.06,0:45:33.81,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.11,0:45:35.51,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}刚才也是  只会添乱
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.04,0:45:40.08,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我要是不去工作  我们连饭都会吃不上！
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.69,0:45:41.65,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.72,0:45:43.33,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么总是让妈妈困扰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.70,0:45:45.67,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.06,0:45:49.42,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}毛毛虫它过来喽！
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.56,0:45:50.93,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}爬来爬去…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.93,0:45:52.58,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}爬来爬去…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.12,0:45:55.42,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}晚饭  买回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.20,0:46:01.13,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾利尔！
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.74,0:46:12.38,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我…  不是妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.36,0:46:15.15,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}做母亲的自觉什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.95,0:46:17.20,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一点都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.33,0:46:20.84,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只是  在过家家而已
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.99,0:46:23.68,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只是因为有米朵帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.66,0:46:26.09,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}绝对不能爱上别人
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.06,0:46:30.41,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这份爱  真的会让你孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.22,0:46:33.17,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的会…
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.78,0:46:35.70,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.42,0:46:51.85,Sayo Asa - chs,昔日织,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&H115E8B&}妈…妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.70,0:46:54.74,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.56,0:47:10.59,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾利尔！
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.87,0:47:16.80,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾利尔！
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.20,0:47:20.25,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在哪…  你在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.36,0:47:21.30,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾利尔！
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.20,0:47:26.19,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾利尔！
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.19,0:47:26.94,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.51,0:47:29.27,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾利尔！
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.90,0:47:37.10,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你上当了！
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.26,0:47:40.40,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以为我金蝉脱壳了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.62,0:47:47.66,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么金蝉脱壳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.96,0:47:49.70,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈笑了！
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.08,0:47:51.94,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾利尔！
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.53,0:47:56.30,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.14,0:47:59.05,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.40,0:48:04.90,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是你…  永远不会长大该多好
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.37,0:48:07.06,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.73,0:48:13.02,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是不长大  就不能保护妈妈了！
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.61,0:48:20.18,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈你又哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.70,0:48:23.94,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不会再哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.55,0:48:26.36,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我可是妈妈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.26,0:48:31.42,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}约好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.91,0:48:32.48,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.78,0:48:43.81,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾利尔  也跟妈妈约好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.24,0:48:45.68,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯  约好了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.64,0:48:49.14,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我会保护好妈妈的
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.94,0:49:06.85,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很好  慢慢推
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.67,0:49:31.98,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快点  出锅了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.55,0:49:33.51,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玛琪娅！
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.18,0:49:34.79,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.48,0:49:40.83,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}之前借我的要好好还啊
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.17,0:49:43.41,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么嘛  就会炫泡到的妹子
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.41,0:49:45.23,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谁炫妹子了  别瞎说！
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.82,0:49:49.00,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这种角度只能靠经验了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.97,0:49:56.27,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以说差不多就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.53,0:49:58.98,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}本来还以为搞得定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.25,0:50:00.53,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}欢迎光临！
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.89,0:50:07.04,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玛琪娅  三份凯尔啤
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.20,0:50:07.92,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.46,0:50:10.37,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}马上来！
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.47,0:50:11.68,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这边也拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.78,0:50:12.44,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.95,0:50:15.89,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小姐姐屁股挺翘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.46,0:50:18.55,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.85,0:50:22.88,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过一点都不像呢  你们俩
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.49,0:50:24.23,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我说
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.78,0:50:28.15,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们来这  也差不多一年了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.80,0:50:30.01,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以前住哪儿啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.83,0:50:34.17,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哎呀  都说你俩是在假装姐弟
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.50,0:50:37.70,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其实是一对私奔的情侣流落到此
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.18,0:50:39.36,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.07,0:50:43.01,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊  多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.16,0:50:46.41,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.95,0:50:51.79,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}又来新的了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.39,0:50:54.97,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们要派多少监工才会满意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.49,0:50:57.65,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嘛  如今毕竟是铁器的时代
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.19,0:51:00.64,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}多亏梅萨特不停的制造大炮
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.70,0:51:02.53,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}咱们才能混口饱饭
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.92,0:51:24.26,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过还是有些不正常啊
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.91,0:51:26.80,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感觉又要打仗了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.43,0:51:30.45,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个呆瓜王子哪里指挥得了军队
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.45,0:51:31.09,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可不嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.75,0:51:39.27,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这里一直都这样
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.76,0:51:41.16,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吵吵闹闹的还请见谅
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.48,0:51:43.60,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天请各位在这里点菜
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.14,0:51:55.19,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玛琪娅！
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.73,0:51:56.73,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}朗格！
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.56,0:52:00.01,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的是玛琪娅
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.01,0:52:01.36,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}完全没变呢
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.51,0:52:02.47,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.94,0:52:04.40,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}朗格你变了好多
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.90,0:52:06.87,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么能长这么高呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.22,0:52:09.34,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别把人说得跟小麦似的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.66,0:52:13.41,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看啊  艾利尔！
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.83,0:52:15.08,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾利尔！
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.88,0:52:18.18,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是朗格  你朗格哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.69,0:52:20.24,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你就是  艾利尔！
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.87,0:52:33.26,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}方便过来打扰吗
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.53,0:52:35.84,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没事的  这儿乱糟糟的抱歉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.68,0:52:37.89,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.28,0:52:39.99,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}米朵和戴奥尔都一切安好
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.37,0:52:41.07,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.43,0:52:44.35,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过  景气的也只有德雷尔这样的大城市
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.93,0:52:46.88,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}乡下早已是老态龙钟
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.83,0:52:49.09,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}戴奥尔也离开了村子
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.20,0:52:50.14,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊  谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.63,0:52:52.26,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}戴奥尔也出去找活了？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.73,0:52:54.48,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不然就活不下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.25,0:52:57.30,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我该出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.22,0:53:01.39,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么  出去泡妞吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.60,0:53:03.78,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}才不是  去值夜班
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.19,0:53:06.80,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}路上小心  艾利尔
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.49,0:53:09.23,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我会为你准备夜宵的
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.78,0:53:21.30,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到这之后  他也开始工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.97,0:53:23.70,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的很努力
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.18,0:53:24.99,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.88,0:53:28.21,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}毕竟不能再卖昔日织了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.62,0:53:33.01,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且因为我的原因  也不能长时间呆在一个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.88,0:53:37.94,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是吗  也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.63,0:53:41.06,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没有血缘关系这件事  他应该
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.35,0:53:42.73,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}已经知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.31,0:53:45.86,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.79,0:53:48.08,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}差不多五年前
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.82,0:53:51.45,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他对我说  想要一个人睡
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.31,0:53:54.41,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也不再叫我妈妈了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.21,0:53:59.25,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「呐」呀    「喂」呀
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.63,0:54:00.85,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就只会这样叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.96,0:54:03.66,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他也到这个年龄了嘛  我那时也是
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.79,0:54:05.74,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}呐  朗格
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.09,0:54:09.47,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你知道  蕾莉雅后来怎么样了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.42,0:54:20.82,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}又死了一头啊
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.72,0:54:27.17,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}将尸骨焚化  然后把骨灰深埋
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.20,0:54:31.34,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.59,0:54:33.71,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没事的  梅朵梅尔大人
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.21,0:54:35.89,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}呐  父亲大人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.04,0:54:38.29,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}海赛尔大人正忙于公务
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.09,0:54:41.98,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.53,0:54:44.67,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}梅朵梅尔大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.37,0:54:48.52,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.33,0:54:54.46,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}发色若霁月银华  双瞳生金轮丽影
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.46,0:54:57.96,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}此外  据传伊尔夫之民躯暖不显
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.09,0:55:01.75,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}梅朵梅尔大人的贵体  并未显现前述体征
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.92,0:55:02.71,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.08,0:55:05.80,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}既不能得长子  又不能继长命
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.80,0:55:08.41,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要那个怪物还有何用
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.68,0:55:13.56,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}梅朵梅尔大人诞世以降  太子妃妊娠愈难
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.78,0:55:17.88,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}海赛尔王子对蕾莉雅妃亦渐生厌恶
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.81,0:55:21.19,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怜我儿海赛尔
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.44,0:55:22.64,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快给我想办法！
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.76,0:55:25.39,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}至少再给我儿寻一个妃子！
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.81,0:55:26.56,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.61,0:55:29.13,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}臣等正在搜寻伊尔夫的遗民
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.17,0:55:31.25,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以继我王血脉
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.43,0:55:33.17,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.44,0:55:34.45,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.12,0:55:38.31,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不打扮得这么花枝招展
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.74,0:55:40.48,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就连抱我一下的心思都没有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.04,0:55:42.89,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那还不如放我走啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.02,0:55:49.08,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅大人她…
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.30,0:55:50.45,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这里就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.89,0:55:58.32,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雷纳托又死了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.29,0:55:59.88,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.39,0:56:03.07,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}自从生下梅朵梅尔
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.59,0:56:06.78,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就一直被幽禁在此
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.15,0:56:09.68,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都不能见她一面
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.50,0:56:13.34,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.54,0:56:16.41,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和雷纳托一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.47,0:56:19.44,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只能存活于传说中的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.94,0:56:21.22,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}作为缥缈的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.47,0:56:25.11,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}长空之中展翼的种族也好
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.08,0:56:27.61,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拂晓时分歌唱的花儿也好
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.34,0:56:30.36,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在这个世界都是活不下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.58,0:56:33.56,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们应该都能抗衡的
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.06,0:56:36.35,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}让那些传说流传后世
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.10,0:56:40.28,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}亏你说得出口
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.09,0:56:46.19,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不正是你把那些传说  给断送了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.60,0:57:07.17,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}请您  让我赎罪
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.17,0:57:08.10,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}开什么玩笑！
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.50,0:57:11.57,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那你就带我去见梅朵梅尔啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.13,0:57:14.05,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么就不让我去见她呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.83,0:57:16.66,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她明明是我的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.97,0:57:21.11,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我都快…  忘记她的味道了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.21,0:57:25.45,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还有抱着她时的那份柔软
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.91,0:57:28.00,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.77,0:57:32.02,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们还要从我这里夺走多少东西！
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.87,0:57:33.98,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.50,0:57:37.25,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想要让我孤身一人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.03,0:57:40.77,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是不让我见梅朵梅尔
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.71,0:57:43.32,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就把玛琪娅带过来
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.31,0:57:48.28,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.04,0:57:50.61,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把伊尔夫一族的玛琪娅…
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.60,0:57:52.26,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.37,0:57:55.94,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不想再孤身一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.54,0:58:09.36,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}收拾得这么起劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.92,0:58:11.82,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们一直不都是两个人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.24,0:58:14.77,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还没有客人来过家里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.38,0:58:20.86,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}呐  能帮我一下吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.09,0:58:32.66,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你又长高了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.12,0:58:34.24,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}又怎么了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.54,0:58:42.29,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玛琪娅  我有话想跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.01,0:58:44.71,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}工作过后  能占用你一点时间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.49,0:58:46.85,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯  但是现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.85,0:58:48.26,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我随便打发打发时间就行
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.32,0:58:51.21,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玛琪娅  快去上菜
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.21,0:58:51.88,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.64,0:59:00.80,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一直以为是你的女人  我们才没出手的
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.21,0:59:02.56,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可不是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.01,0:59:06.07,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}咱们这儿好男人要多少有多少  是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.29,0:59:09.31,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那种家伙怎么可能得手
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.49,0:59:11.20,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个人不是你们说的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.08,0:59:13.05,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.60,0:59:15.20,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别这么沉重嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.63,0:59:16.84,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}来  喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.52,0:59:18.43,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不  我还…
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.72,0:59:20.36,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你已经不是小鬼了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.01,0:59:27.23,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.33,0:59:29.09,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很好  那这个也能喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.75,0:59:33.13,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}来  成为一个大人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.29,0:59:35.33,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喔喔喔喔！
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.38,0:59:37.26,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是男人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.33,0:59:39.13,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}燃起来！  锤起来！
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.28,0:59:41.17,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}燃起来！  锤起来！
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.30,0:59:43.20,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嘿咻！  嘿咻！
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.25,0:59:45.19,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嘿咻！  嘿咻！
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.25,0:59:46.77,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好样的！
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.02,0:59:48.31,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可以的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.31,0:59:49.71,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就再来一碗
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.18,0:59:52.26,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}做个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.05,0:59:58.40,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们在找我？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.15,1:00:03.28,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看来  这个城市也待不下去了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.43,1:00:06.79,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要和我一块回农场吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.09,1:00:08.68,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}诶  可是…
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.73,1:00:09.83,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}总会有办法的
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.24,1:00:11.98,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}羊奶的价格也涨起来了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.56,1:00:13.79,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾利尔也一起…
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.48,1:00:15.99,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不能再给你们添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.34,1:00:17.15,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玛琪娅
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.68,1:00:21.24,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是把米朵和戴奥尔也卷进去的话
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.21,1:00:23.06,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我该…
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.55,1:00:25.29,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.70,1:00:28.05,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想让你添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.86,1:00:31.25,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}从小时候起就一直
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.93,1:00:34.03,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想帮玛琪娅你做点什么
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.82,1:00:37.34,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好好考虑一下吧  玛琪娅
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.88,1:00:39.88,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不管是今后的事
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.63,1:00:41.26,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还是…
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.46,1:00:44.45,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们的事
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.95,1:01:03.12,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的不行
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.52,1:01:04.43,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}思之再三
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.45,1:01:09.82,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只有艾利尔  我一直念挂在心
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.91,1:01:14.74,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}该怎么样才能和艾利尔一起生活下去
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.13,1:01:19.00,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}该怎么样才能真正成为一个妈妈
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.42,1:01:24.12,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是  完全找不到答案
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.83,1:01:29.94,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}或者说  依旧还在寻找
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.50,1:01:35.14,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}毕竟  我不怎么聪明
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.42,1:01:39.58,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只有艾利尔的事情  我想在今后
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.66,1:01:42.11,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也一直念挂下去
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.65,1:01:49.52,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.55,1:01:51.23,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.20,1:01:56.30,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}至少让我帮忙找一下此后的去处和工作吧
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.20,1:01:58.57,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要总是一个人背负
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.42,1:02:31.28,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾利尔？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.04,1:02:37.31,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在干什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.92,1:02:40.08,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么一身酒气
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.67,1:02:41.83,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我回来了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.01,1:02:43.46,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}说什么「我回来了」
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.72,1:02:44.79,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你怎么了  艾利尔
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.79,1:02:46.29,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}欢迎回家的吻呢
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.28,1:02:51.33,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}过去的话  明明一定会有
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.94,1:02:55.65,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.59,1:02:58.48,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}呐  站得起来吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.12,1:03:04.08,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}咱们  被别人说是私奔流落到这儿的
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.73,1:03:08.41,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}说你会被别的男人给抢走
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.72,1:03:11.03,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在说什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.24,1:03:12.04,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是的
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.21,1:03:12.98,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}站起来
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.55,1:03:15.21,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要睡觉就乖乖去床上
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.26,1:03:26.22,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能走吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.75,1:03:34.65,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要踩！
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.12,1:03:42.89,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这个…
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.64,1:03:46.57,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是艾利尔织给我的吗
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.58,1:03:53.47,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我受够了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.27,1:03:58.31,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么要珍藏这种东西啊
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.45,1:04:01.20,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}总是把我当小孩！
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.54,1:04:31.01,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}它永远都是
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.65,1:04:37.07,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我最珍贵的宝物
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.44,1:04:42.31,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾利尔！
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.80,1:04:49.11,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个  艾利尔
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.80,1:04:52.33,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们  又要搬家了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.22,1:04:55.77,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}接下来你想去哪？
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.39,1:04:58.02,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的话  去哪儿都行
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.56,1:05:00.99,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要能和艾利尔在一起
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.71,1:05:03.68,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我啊
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.57,1:05:07.44,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}从没把你当做是母亲
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.65,1:05:35.01,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想受雇做城里的卫兵
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.55,1:05:37.14,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能请你帮我说说情吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.20,1:05:42.26,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拜托了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.33,1:05:44.98,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玛琪娅会伤心的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.82,1:05:47.23,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她又不是我母亲
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.86,1:05:49.86,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你说了吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.15,1:05:53.77,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你把那句话跟玛琪娅说了吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.80,1:05:55.68,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}说了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.89,1:05:59.06,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你以为
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.52,1:06:02.34,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玛琪娅是怀着怎样的心情把你养大的啊！
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.74,1:06:04.69,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别在这给我撒娇！
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.49,1:06:07.14,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}从你这般年纪开始
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.30,1:06:09.65,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玛琪娅就拼命地想要做好母亲
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.17,1:06:10.99,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你知道吗！
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.09,1:06:12.89,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊啊  我不知道啊！
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.01,1:06:19.65,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么那个人…  要如此的珍爱我
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.58,1:06:24.50,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾利尔
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.25,1:06:26.93,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她总是陪伴着我
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.86,1:06:30.17,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}总是为了我而不顾一切
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.25,1:06:34.52,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我一直以为这样的人就是所谓的母亲
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.46,1:06:38.12,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以  我一直叫她妈妈
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.46,1:06:42.77,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一直想要保护她
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.95,1:06:49.68,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是  现在的我保护不了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.76,1:06:52.00,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不仅如此
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.87,1:06:54.91,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还会伤害到她
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.23,1:06:58.55,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我总算意识到这些了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.81,1:07:03.26,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我根本…  就保护不了她啊！
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.39,1:07:18.30,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样哇哇大哭的你
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.14,1:07:20.85,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的和小时候一模一样啊
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.60,1:07:27.85,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样  真的好吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.77,1:07:49.85,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不用了  我自己来
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.27,1:07:51.80,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不是也要离开城市吗
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.73,1:07:54.89,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想先送走艾利尔
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.09,1:08:09.20,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}路上小心  艾利尔
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.95,1:08:12.98,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一路顺风
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.65,1:08:19.54,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我走了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.98,1:08:58.11,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不…哭
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.40,1:08:59.38,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不哭
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.32,1:09:01.37,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们约好了的
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.78,1:09:07.73,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你骗我  艾利尔
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.78,1:09:10.80,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是约好要保护我的吗
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.31,1:09:15.33,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你骗我…
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.76,1:09:18.80,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不要
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.42,1:10:33.52,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么啊
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.89,1:10:36.60,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还以为能看到真的雷纳托呢
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.88,1:10:38.32,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.45,1:10:43.31,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以前虽然有很多  现在城里就只剩一头了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.51,1:10:47.36,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}靠这种装模作样的雷纳托列队行进
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.44,1:10:49.92,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还想鼓舞士气  怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.56,1:10:52.01,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}说起来你知道吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.40,1:10:54.99,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}听说拜埃拉搞到伊尔夫了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.04,1:10:56.82,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拜埃拉？ 真的吗
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.39,1:11:04.11,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}师团长阁下  别再烤虱子了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.62,1:11:05.37,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}闭嘴！
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.96,1:11:06.99,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}朗格师团长
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.87,1:11:12.73,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的  确实在找
Dialogue: 0,1:11:13.59,1:11:16.66,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}听说是和蕾莉雅妃看起来差不多大的少女
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.23,1:11:21.02,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不一定就是玛琪娅
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.16,1:11:23.00,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你担心吗
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.15,1:11:25.00,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个人
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.63,1:11:26.78,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是很坚强的
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.03,1:11:31.39,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玛琪娅要是听到了  一定会高兴的
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.35,1:11:36.81,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她一直为自己能不能保护好艾利尔  而感到不安
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.89,1:11:38.89,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}即便如此依然拼尽全力
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.83,1:11:44.18,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想让你觉得  她是个可靠又坚强的母亲
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.45,1:11:47.29,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是个小鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.65,1:11:54.18,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}或许  我还是个小鬼
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.33,1:11:55.99,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.60,1:11:59.02,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也会成为一个父亲
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.57,1:12:08.71,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}梅萨特
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.17,1:12:10.58,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这个外强中干的国度
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.11,1:12:13.80,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}窃上古之力以为威权
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.01,1:12:16.72,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}亵渎传说  何其愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.46,1:12:21.17,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我等定会全力协助阁下
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.12,1:12:41.86,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玛琪娅
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.02,1:12:44.42,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}总算准备好了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.58,1:12:47.77,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}头发都这么长了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.70,1:12:51.05,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}伊尔夫的子民若要长发及腰
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.41,1:12:52.61,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}必须诞下孩子
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.30,1:12:55.19,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}来吧  玛琪娅
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.86,1:12:57.30,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}让我们去迎接蕾莉雅
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.50,1:13:07.89,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要打仗了吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.70,1:13:10.58,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}痛苦也不过是一时而已
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.41,1:13:12.94,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且这些年来
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.26,1:13:15.35,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不是承受了更为深切的痛苦吗
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.52,1:13:20.32,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}离开了伊尔夫  近乎失去一切
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.85,1:13:23.54,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}行尸走肉一般的栖于窖穴…
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.74,1:13:25.46,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你啊
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.75,1:13:29.20,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}总算能理解我们的心情了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.03,1:13:31.60,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大家辗转零落
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.87,1:13:34.93,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}长老大人  恐怕也已经不在人世了
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.26,1:13:38.97,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们深谙无凭之苦
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.81,1:13:40.82,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而在这时
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.57,1:13:44.06,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只有你与幸福相伴
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.23,1:13:48.56,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}伊尔夫的子民  大家都共执机枢
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.24,1:13:51.36,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我和蕾莉雅  还有玛琪娅
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.71,1:13:54.72,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我等往昔既然同工  明朝又怎能异曲
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.13,1:14:06.65,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}恭喜你  玛琪娅
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.30,1:14:09.95,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如此一来  你独有的往昔已然随风而逝
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.62,1:14:14.10,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们仍将音出一律  共织未来
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.01,1:14:36.81,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蒂塔！
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.44,1:14:40.05,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你回来啦  艾利尔
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.53,1:14:47.57,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天这么早就回来了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.90,1:14:49.32,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明明是这么关键的时候
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.43,1:14:50.73,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我却这么忙碌实在抱歉
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.76,1:14:54.51,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}说是  距离分娩还有一段时间
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.97,1:14:57.35,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过  还是会担心的
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.21,1:14:59.53,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}晚饭马上就好
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.13,1:15:02.80,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不用了  不要勉强  我来做吧
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.57,1:15:05.85,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我还想稍微活动一下呢
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.79,1:15:09.77,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好啦  坐吧坐吧
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.89,1:15:17.33,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}总算快要生了  真是不可思议
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.41,1:15:22.30,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为了找工作  来到梅萨特
Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.01,1:15:25.03,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然后和艾利尔重逢
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.56,1:15:27.41,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且还…
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.29,1:15:31.27,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}呐  艾利尔
Dialogue: 0,1:15:32.48,1:15:34.23,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}选择我真的好吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.97,1:15:39.55,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.44,1:16:07.23,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拜埃拉吗
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.82,1:16:09.28,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不只是拜埃拉的船
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.06,1:16:11.92,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}优格的也有  恩多拉的也有！
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.56,1:16:19.89,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾利尔  等等
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.33,1:16:23.48,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你一定要保护好肚子里的孩子
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.88,1:16:42.88,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}来得太迟了  艾利尔
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.30,1:16:44.13,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.24,1:16:54.70,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}据报  拜埃拉军已经越过山口
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.10,1:16:55.90,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们要兵分两路…
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.51,1:17:02.51,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是讽刺啊
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.65,1:17:15.81,旁白/独白 - chs,旁白/独白,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}梅萨特  为炫耀其威权  利用了上古之力
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.67,1:17:17.79,旁白/独白 - chs,旁白/独白,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}然而事与愿违
Dialogue: 0,1:17:18.28,1:17:21.61,旁白/独白 - chs,旁白/独白,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}其自身因滥用上古之力
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.94,1:17:25.03,旁白/独白 - chs,旁白/独白,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}而为周边各国联手制裁
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.41,1:17:36.91,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大臣都去哪了！
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.53,1:17:40.85,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}听说  他们已经和随从离开王城了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.82,1:17:43.61,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们是要抛弃我吗
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.07,1:17:45.94,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这该如何是好！
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.90,1:17:49.88,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们已经完了  要永别了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:51.00,1:17:52.62,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}陛下  请您赶快
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.13,1:17:55.28,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂  梅朵梅尔大人怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.24,1:17:57.62,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这种不详的名字
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.74,1:18:00.96,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们才不需要  和她妈一块丢掉啊！
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.69,1:18:52.96,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玛琪娅  我们走
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.89,1:19:29.64,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾利尔！
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.63,1:19:33.23,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾利尔！
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.44,1:19:52.21,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.01,1:19:55.10,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}终于找到你了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.85,1:19:58.77,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}克里姆？
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.50,1:20:01.38,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么…
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.98,1:20:04.00,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你还活着？
Dialogue: 0,1:20:05.26,1:20:07.61,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我  这是看到了…
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.33,1:20:12.35,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}亡灵吗
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.89,1:20:18.97,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我来接你了
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.80,1:20:21.57,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在这之后
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.51,1:20:24.37,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那些让你受苦的家伙
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.14,1:20:27.17,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}定要让他们痛彻心扉
Dialogue: 0,1:20:28.08,1:20:30.93,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然后让一切…  都重新来过
Dialogue: 0,1:20:31.00,1:20:31.70,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.24,1:20:36.17,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我好想见见
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.09,1:20:39.01,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的女儿
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.53,1:20:41.78,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.73,1:20:45.99,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那不是他们强迫你生下的  违心的存在吗
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.32,1:20:48.63,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是  那是我生下的…
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.63,1:20:49.84,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}忘掉不就行了！
Dialogue: 0,1:20:50.39,1:20:53.58,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要你的昔日织上  未曾刻下她的名字
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.84,1:20:54.99,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可…  可是
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.58,1:21:02.90,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我原以为克里姆  还都大家  都死了
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.80,1:21:13.06,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以为自己已经失去一切了
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.88,1:21:18.28,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以  只有女儿  我一直念挂在心
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.75,1:21:22.24,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想要见见她
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.94,1:21:25.95,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想要抱抱她
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.18,1:21:31.32,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就只为这一点念想  我才苟活到了今天
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.88,1:21:34.71,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.77,1:21:40.20,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的…  梅朵梅尔
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.58,1:21:56.54,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道了  蕾莉雅
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.83,1:21:59.74,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就一起
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.86,1:22:01.89,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在此走向终结吧
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.80,1:22:06.60,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}克里姆
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.40,1:22:13.21,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不会再让…
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.80,1:22:20.04,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那些家伙…
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.06,1:22:27.06,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}继续玷污  我们的昔日织了
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.29,1:22:36.10,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}克里姆
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.03,1:22:41.07,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅大人！
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.41,1:23:14.85,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.01,1:23:17.06,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅也好
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.72,1:23:18.67,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玛琪娅也好
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.40,1:23:20.36,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.86,1:23:25.27,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么她们  都要让时光流转
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.00,1:24:05.88,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这就像…  那天一样
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.19,1:24:33.83,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾利尔
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.97,1:24:36.90,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}师团长阁下
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.89,1:24:42.20,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}据报  拜埃拉的船里有一对伊尔夫的少男少女
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.74,1:24:46.26,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们  见到了吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.01,1:24:49.61,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.01,1:24:51.78,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你可以回去了
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.14,1:24:54.10,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这里就交给我们  快去玛琪娅…
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.10,1:24:55.14,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我要继续战斗！
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.48,1:24:58.80,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你对梅萨特就那么忠诚吗
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.23,1:25:00.03,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}恐怕不是吧
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.37,1:25:02.34,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不过是想从玛琪娅身边逃开…
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.34,1:25:02.97,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是的！
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.70,1:25:07.04,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}的确  开始的时候是那样的
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.16,1:25:10.62,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但如今  我有了蒂塔
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.35,1:25:12.30,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有了伙伴
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.07,1:25:14.67,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还有快要出生的宝宝
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.90,1:25:16.77,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这个梅萨特
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.49,1:25:18.82,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在我离开那个人以后
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.06,1:25:21.21,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}已然成为我亲手创造的最初的归宿
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.64,1:25:22.95,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我一定要保护好他们！
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.71,1:25:44.78,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.29,1:25:52.00,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不是…
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.05,1:25:52.79,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我去找医生！
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.22,1:25:53.97,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不行
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.33,1:25:57.13,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在这种时候…
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.38,1:25:57.98,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.46,1:26:01.58,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是艾利尔的
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.60,1:26:03.61,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小宝宝
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.41,1:26:11.34,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}放！
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.73,1:26:32.94,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}放！
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.03,1:26:37.70,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蒂塔
Dialogue: 0,1:26:39.68,1:26:41.81,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}加油  很快就能
Dialogue: 0,1:26:42.59,1:26:43.98,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}见到小宝宝了
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.92,1:27:06.27,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对对  真棒
Dialogue: 0,1:27:07.66,1:27:09.69,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蒂塔  还有一点点
Dialogue: 0,1:27:11.62,1:27:12.86,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就剩一点点了
Dialogue: 0,1:27:14.58,1:27:15.22,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蒂塔！
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.37,1:27:23.46,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都别怕！
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.25,1:27:33.88,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我好怕…
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.91,1:27:36.44,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蒂塔
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.44,1:27:38.21,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我怕…  我怕！
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.40,1:27:40.11,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}救救我…
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.11,1:27:41.58,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蒂塔  没事的
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.98,1:27:42.37,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\an1\blur3}小宝宝
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.76,1:27:45.69,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}救救我的小宝宝啊！
Dialogue: 0,1:27:45.69,1:27:46.60,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我会救你们的
Dialogue: 0,1:27:47.96,1:27:48.77,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们会得救的！
Dialogue: 0,1:27:51.90,1:27:54.26,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}黎明就在眼前  杀进去！
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.88,1:28:10.96,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看  小宝宝他
Dialogue: 0,1:28:11.35,1:28:12.86,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}正急着想见妈妈呢
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.15,1:28:20.18,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蒂塔和艾利尔  就要做妈妈和爸爸了
Dialogue: 0,1:28:51.83,1:28:53.84,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你很努力呢  蒂塔
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.20,1:28:56.08,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}新妈妈
Dialogue: 0,1:29:14.25,1:29:16.09,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你还打算带他走吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.84,1:29:17.86,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这可不是玩具…
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.86,1:29:19.00,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他不是玩具
Dialogue: 0,1:29:19.41,1:29:20.31,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他是我的
Dialogue: 0,1:29:21.40,1:29:22.56,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}昔日织啊
Dialogue: 0,1:29:25.74,1:29:26.61,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,1:29:29.03,1:29:29.97,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.31,1:29:43.96,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾利尔  该回家了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.93,1:29:46.36,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈！
Dialogue: 0,1:29:46.80,1:29:48.26,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我回来了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:52.09,1:29:53.88,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都冻成这样了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.94,1:29:58.95,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你回来啦  艾利尔
Dialogue: 0,1:30:06.77,1:30:07.64,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你回来啦
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.34,1:30:11.19,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾利尔
Dialogue: 0,1:30:15.27,1:30:15.97,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}梦…
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.93,1:30:18.29,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这不是梦
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.39,1:30:21.84,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是  下雪了
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.64,1:30:25.19,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这不是雪  是灰
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.82,1:30:39.83,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾利尔和蒂塔的小宝宝  已经出生了
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.35,1:30:44.31,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}现在不要勉强
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.00,1:30:47.87,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}放心吧  她们会等着艾利尔回去的
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.37,1:30:50.81,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她们两人  会一直等着你
Dialogue: 0,1:30:53.76,1:30:55.23,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾利尔也是那样
Dialogue: 0,1:30:56.24,1:30:58.27,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}从妈妈肚子里生下来的呢
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.56,1:31:06.05,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾利尔的妈妈啊
Dialogue: 0,1:31:06.94,1:31:10.72,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把艾利尔  抱得好紧好紧
Dialogue: 0,1:31:12.18,1:31:15.04,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}十根手指  扣得那么有力
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.90,1:31:17.49,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}费了好大力气才掰开
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.97,1:31:21.41,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一根…  一根…
Dialogue: 0,1:31:21.95,1:31:22.77,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别说了
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.87,1:31:23.62,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我啊
Dialogue: 0,1:31:25.15,1:31:28.34,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还是没能  成为艾利尔的妈妈呢
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.34,1:31:29.33,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要再说了！
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.80,1:31:33.43,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是你教会了我
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.28,1:31:35.15,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}温柔
Dialogue: 0,1:31:35.88,1:31:36.76,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}坚强
Dialogue: 0,1:31:37.50,1:31:38.34,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}勇敢
Dialogue: 0,1:31:39.70,1:31:41.80,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还有爱人之心
Dialogue: 0,1:31:47.88,1:31:49.89,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为艾利尔着想
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.89,1:31:53.51,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就像是为我自己着想一样
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.86,1:31:57.57,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}刚遇到艾利尔的时候
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.32,1:32:01.88,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就想  这孩子一定能伴我饮泣
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.30,1:32:06.19,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还想着  他就是我的昔日织
Dialogue: 0,1:32:09.11,1:32:10.72,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要能和艾利尔在一起
Dialogue: 0,1:32:11.35,1:32:14.84,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那形形色色的悲伤  还有痛苦
Dialogue: 0,1:32:16.02,1:32:17.32,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都能归于平静
Dialogue: 0,1:32:19.28,1:32:21.39,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然而  我却…
Dialogue: 0,1:32:22.05,1:32:22.90,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}从你身边…
Dialogue: 0,1:32:24.75,1:32:26.96,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾利尔从来都没有骗过我
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.41,1:32:31.81,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾利尔一直都遵守着约定
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.84,1:32:36.69,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一直都在保护着我
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.16,1:32:41.21,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}纵使天各一方  兀自流浪
Dialogue: 0,1:32:41.84,1:32:44.24,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哪怕自己不知所向
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.60,1:32:48.31,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}即便如此  只要想起了艾利尔
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.75,1:32:51.04,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就仍然是我
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.70,1:32:55.04,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要艾利尔愿意叫我
Dialogue: 0,1:32:55.69,1:32:57.79,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哪怕不是「妈妈」我也愿意
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.76,1:33:00.08,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不管叫我什么
Dialogue: 0,1:33:00.82,1:33:04.52,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个名字  也一定会是我的名字
Dialogue: 0,1:33:06.40,1:33:11.03,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}正是艾利尔你  织出了如今的我
Dialogue: 0,1:33:22.11,1:33:22.93,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玛琪娅！
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.51,1:33:28.33,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}朗格！
Dialogue: 0,1:33:29.22,1:33:31.28,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能帮我把艾利尔带回去吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:33:33.06,1:33:34.86,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}回到到蒂塔和小宝宝那里
Dialogue: 0,1:33:36.39,1:33:38.71,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}回到艾利尔的归宿
Dialogue: 0,1:33:50.42,1:33:51.39,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要走…
Dialogue: 0,1:33:59.79,1:34:00.93,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要走啊！
Dialogue: 0,1:34:01.70,1:34:02.92,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈！
Dialogue: 0,1:35:10.14,1:35:13.05,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们差不多该下去了  梅朵梅尔大人
Dialogue: 0,1:35:13.54,1:35:15.00,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}父亲大人他们呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:35:19.12,1:35:21.62,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样啊  没关系的
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.33,1:35:24.80,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}从这里下去以后
Dialogue: 0,1:35:25.05,1:35:28.05,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等待着我的一定是完全不同的生活
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.20,1:35:32.08,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是  即便如此  我也…
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.74,1:35:49.97,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,1:35:53.24,1:35:54.50,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅大人
Dialogue: 0,1:36:00.41,1:36:01.40,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你就是…
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.41,1:36:05.14,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的…  妈妈
Dialogue: 0,1:36:10.37,1:36:12.31,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是伊尔夫的蕾莉雅
Dialogue: 0,1:36:14.11,1:36:18.51,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是个野姑娘  疯丫头  女丈夫
Dialogue: 0,1:36:20.87,1:36:21.80,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.83,1:36:23.78,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}自由不羁
Dialogue: 0,1:36:27.44,1:36:29.03,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅  飞起来！
Dialogue: 0,1:36:43.64,1:36:45.73,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是…  会飞的！
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.24,1:36:50.37,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈！
Dialogue: 0,1:37:08.80,1:37:09.62,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玛琪娅
Dialogue: 0,1:37:12.25,1:37:13.04,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,1:37:14.45,1:37:15.98,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你也飞起来了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:37:22.74,1:37:23.80,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再见了！
Dialogue: 0,1:37:24.50,1:37:26.20,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}忘掉我吧
Dialogue: 0,1:37:26.77,1:37:28.16,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也会忘掉
Dialogue: 0,1:37:28.93,1:37:31.81,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}无论是王城的日子  还是此刻的晨曦
Dialogue: 0,1:37:31.93,1:37:33.40,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我都不会记在昔日织里！
Dialogue: 0,1:37:33.96,1:37:34.99,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.53,1:37:39.16,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在漫长而悠久的记忆中  将它忘却
Dialogue: 0,1:37:40.12,1:37:41.65,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我会忘掉的
Dialogue: 0,1:37:42.98,1:37:43.46,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的…
Dialogue: 0,1:37:44.58,1:37:46.42,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这只是个小小的缝口！
Dialogue: 0,1:37:51.59,1:37:52.07,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}呐
Dialogue: 0,1:37:52.79,1:37:53.27,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.79,1:37:57.60,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}母亲大人她  真是位漂亮的人啊
Dialogue: 0,1:38:01.94,1:38:03.07,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}梅朵梅尔大人
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.03,1:38:06.94,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是雷纳托！
Dialogue: 0,1:38:12.86,1:38:14.01,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅大人…
Dialogue: 0,1:38:16.35,1:38:17.66,旁白/独白 - chs,旁白/独白,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}不需要什么雷纳托
Dialogue: 0,1:38:18.64,1:38:19.94,旁白/独白 - chs,旁白/独白,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}不需要什么伊尔夫
Dialogue: 0,1:38:20.69,1:38:23.33,旁白/独白 - chs,旁白/独白,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}这些上古存世的种族注定会走向灭亡
Dialogue: 0,1:38:24.24,1:38:24.88,旁白/独白 - chs,旁白/独白,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}既然如此
Dialogue: 0,1:38:25.81,1:38:28.35,旁白/独白 - chs,旁白/独白,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}至少最后  让她们放飞心灵
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.34,1:38:36.31,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别哭了  蕾莉雅
Dialogue: 0,1:38:41.29,1:38:44.57,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}放心吧  绝对不会忘记的
Dialogue: 0,1:38:56.59,1:38:57.77,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我好难过
Dialogue: 0,1:38:59.93,1:39:02.15,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好心酸…  好痛苦…
Dialogue: 0,1:39:04.43,1:39:06.98,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是  世界是如此的美丽…
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.94,1:39:09.70,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么可能将它忘却
Dialogue: 0,1:39:42.80,1:39:43.65,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我回来了
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.31,1:39:47.57,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你回来了
Dialogue: 0,1:39:49.34,1:39:50.50,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这不是理所当然的吗
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.12,1:39:54.91,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的…
Dialogue: 0,1:40:05.39,1:40:07.39,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这么柔弱  好可怕
Dialogue: 0,1:40:13.62,1:40:15.76,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}名字  得取一个呢
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.15,1:40:18.84,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蒂塔？
Dialogue: 0,1:40:19.94,1:40:20.93,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:40:22.63,1:40:24.17,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在我们小时候
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.39,1:40:29.65,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我说过「男孩怎么会喜欢妈妈」
Dialogue: 0,1:40:30.89,1:40:31.89,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样的话
Dialogue: 0,1:40:33.84,1:40:35.52,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明明一点都不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,1:40:36.41,1:40:38.42,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾利尔的妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,1:40:38.99,1:40:40.17,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是那么的美丽
Dialogue: 0,1:40:41.03,1:40:42.17,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那么的温柔
Dialogue: 0,1:40:44.13,1:40:44.81,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我却…
Dialogue: 0,1:40:49.05,1:40:51.01,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}刚才  这孩子也是…
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.38,1:40:52.12,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我爱你
Dialogue: 0,1:40:53.68,1:40:54.82,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也是…
Dialogue: 0,1:40:55.94,1:40:56.97,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是我…
Dialogue: 0,1:40:57.95,1:41:01.52,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一直  都嫉妒着艾利尔的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,1:41:04.26,1:41:08.16,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈养大的我  会永远爱你
Dialogue: 0,1:41:10.12,1:41:12.62,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这孩子  也一定会和人邂逅
Dialogue: 0,1:41:13.70,1:41:15.41,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把她养大吧  我们一起
Dialogue: 0,1:41:16.78,1:41:19.13,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我和蒂塔  我们两个人
Dialogue: 0,1:41:20.41,1:41:23.72,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这孩子  也一定会爱上他人
Dialogue: 0,1:41:30.03,1:41:31.40,旁白/独白 - chs,旁白/独白,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}离别一族
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.16,1:41:35.17,旁白/独白 - chs,旁白/独白,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}送走人间种种别离
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.21,1:41:38.08,旁白/独白 - chs,旁白/独白,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}总走人世种种变迁
Dialogue: 0,1:41:39.33,1:41:42.56,旁白/独白 - chs,旁白/独白,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}时光流转  永不驻足
Dialogue: 0,1:41:44.54,1:41:47.61,旁白/独白 - chs,旁白/独白,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}所以  我们将再次邂逅
Dialogue: 0,1:41:49.97,1:41:50.86,旁白/独白 - chs,旁白/独白,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}再次结缘
Dialogue: 0,1:41:52.12,1:41:53.25,旁白/独白 - chs,旁白/独白,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}再次执梭成布
Dialogue: 0,1:42:08.56,1:42:09.54,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你好啊
Dialogue: 0,1:42:13.58,1:42:16.49,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能带我  去你爷爷那里吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:42:17.52,1:42:18.66,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我爷爷？
Dialogue: 0,1:42:18.77,1:42:19.92,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}莉莉！
Dialogue: 0,1:42:20.45,1:42:22.81,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这么能这样呢  一直在这儿吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:42:25.16,1:42:26.09,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是…
Dialogue: 0,1:42:30.06,1:42:32.59,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}母亲三年前就过世了
Dialogue: 0,1:42:33.29,1:42:35.09,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们彼此非常恩爱
Dialogue: 0,1:42:35.84,1:42:37.46,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}梅萨特陷落之后
Dialogue: 0,1:42:37.86,1:42:40.28,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在朗格先生的帮助下回到了这里
Dialogue: 0,1:42:41.72,1:42:43.25,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}虽然经历了风风雨雨
Dialogue: 0,1:42:43.65,1:42:45.78,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我相信他们的人生是幸福的
Dialogue: 0,1:42:52.58,1:42:54.06,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别急  别急
Dialogue: 0,1:42:54.06,1:42:56.60,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们经常说起您的事情
Dialogue: 0,1:42:57.39,1:42:59.56,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}两个人都  一脸幸福
Dialogue: 0,1:43:00.69,1:43:02.37,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能赶上真的太好了
Dialogue: 0,1:43:03.27,1:43:04.87,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}父亲他  已经…
Dialogue: 0,1:43:35.63,1:43:36.47,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我回来了
Dialogue: 0,1:43:37.16,1:43:37.97,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾利尔
Dialogue: 0,1:43:48.65,1:43:50.90,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真了不起  艾利尔
Dialogue: 0,1:43:55.40,1:43:56.28,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是这么…
Dialogue: 0,1:44:00.29,1:44:04.03,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}努力地  活完了一生呢
Dialogue: 0,1:44:04.46,1:44:05.29,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾利尔
Dialogue: 0,1:44:11.13,1:44:12.19,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不哭
Dialogue: 0,1:44:13.14,1:44:15.44,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们  约好了的
Dialogue: 0,1:44:29.75,1:44:33.67,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你回来…了…
Dialogue: 0,1:44:42.38,1:44:43.35,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我回来了
Dialogue: 0,1:45:32.17,1:45:34.42,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}路上小心  艾利尔
Dialogue: 0,1:45:36.26,1:45:37.70,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}晚饭之前
Dialogue: 0,1:45:38.50,1:45:39.92,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一定要回来啊
Dialogue: 0,1:45:46.31,1:45:47.22,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}送给你
Dialogue: 0,1:45:48.13,1:45:49.16,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:46:10.04,1:46:12.89,Sayo Asa - chs,往昔,0,0,0,,{\move(920,1020,1000,1020)\fad(200,200)\blur3\1a&H1A&}妈妈！  妈妈！
