Dialogue: 0,1:46:17.62,1:46:18.37,Sayo Asa - chs,往昔,0,0,0,,{\move(920,1020,1000,1020)\fad(200,200)\blur3\1a&H1A&}早上好！
Dialogue: 0,1:46:19.57,1:46:20.85,Sayo Asa - chs,往昔,0,0,0,,{\move(920,1020,1000,1020)\fad(200,200)\blur3\1a&H1A&}你上当了！
Dialogue: 0,1:46:20.78,1:46:22.93,Sayo Asa - chs,往昔,0,0,0,,{\move(920,1020,1000,1020)\fad(200,200)\blur3\1a&H1A&}以为我金蝉脱壳了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:46:22.82,1:46:24.41,Sayo Asa - chs,往昔,0,0,0,,{\move(920,1020,1000,1020)\fad(200,200)\blur3\1a&H1A&}那我出生的地方呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:46:24.33,1:46:26.65,Sayo Asa - chs,往昔,0,0,0,,{\move(920,1020,1000,1020)\fad(200,200)\blur3\1a&H1A&}毛毛虫它过来啦！
Dialogue: 0,1:46:26.48,1:46:28.01,Sayo Asa - chs,往昔,0,0,0,,{\move(920,1020,1000,1020)\fad(200,200)\blur3\1a&H1A&}妈妈笑了！
Dialogue: 0,1:46:28.82,1:46:31.06,Sayo Asa - chs,往昔,0,0,0,,{\move(920,1020,1000,1020)\fad(200,200)\blur3\1a&H1A&}妈妈和大家不一样
Dialogue: 0,1:46:30.50,1:46:31.71,Sayo Asa - chs,往昔,0,0,0,,{\move(920,1020,1000,1020)\fad(200,200)\blur3\1a&H1A&}妈妈  快看快看
Dialogue: 0,1:46:31.39,1:46:32.69,Sayo Asa - chs,往昔,0,0,0,,{\move(920,1020,1000,1020)\fad(200,200)\blur3\1a&H1A&}呐  快看嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:46:32.62,1:46:34.15,Sayo Asa - chs,往昔,0,0,0,,{\move(920,1020,1000,1020)\fad(200,200)\blur3\1a&H1A&}妈妈  为什么
Dialogue: 0,1:46:35.22,1:46:37.84,Sayo Asa - chs,往昔,0,0,0,,{\move(920,1020,1000,1020)\fad(200,200)\blur3\1a&H1A&}在这里的话  就不像妈妈了
Dialogue: 0,1:46:37.74,1:46:40.41,Sayo Asa - chs,往昔,0,0,0,,{\move(920,1020,1000,1020)\fad(200,200)\blur3\1a&H1A&}不许你惹妈妈哭
Dialogue: 0,1:46:40.41,1:46:42.64,Sayo Asa - chs,往昔,0,0,0,,{\move(920,1020,1000,1020)\fad(200,200)\blur3\1a&H1A&}我呢  只要妈妈在就好
