Dialogue: 0,1:48:45.38,1:48:46.96,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要笑我啊
Dialogue: 0,1:48:47.26,1:48:49.29,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}长老要是看到你这张脸
